  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>An unenhanced weapon you touch becomes an enhanced weapon. Choose one of these damage types: acid, cold, energy, fire, ion, kinetic, or lightning. For the duration, an unenhanced weapon you touch has a +1 to attack rolls and deals an extra [[/r 1d4]] damage of the chosen type.</p>\n<p><strong><em>Overcharge Tech.</em></strong> When you cast this power using a 5th or 6th level tech slot, the bonus to attack rolls increases to +2 and the extra damage increases to [[/r 2d4]]. When you use a slot of 7th level or higher, the bonus increases to +3 and the extra damage increases to [[/r 3d4]].</p>",
